---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = 'Boho Wedding Invitations | Hummingbird Social Studio';
const description = 'Boho wedding invitation suites inspired by earthy colors, wildflowers, desert weddings, natural textures, and relaxed romantic wedding design.';
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Boho Wedding Invitations</h1>

    <p>
      Earthy color palettes, romantic floral details, natural textures, and effortless design.
      Our boho wedding invitation suites are inspired by wildflowers, desert landscapes,
      outdoor venues, soft neutrals, and relaxed modern romance.
    </p>

    <p>
      Whether you are planning a desert wedding, backyard celebration, mountain ceremony,
      or intimate outdoor gathering, these invitation suites are designed to feel warm,
      organic, personal, and beautifully intentional.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="content-section">
  <div class="container">

    <h2>Inspired by Natural, Romantic Design</h2>

    <p>
      Boho weddings are known for their relaxed style, layered textures, earthy tones,
      and creative details. These invitation suites often include soft typography,
      botanical illustrations, muted colors, handmade-inspired layouts, and natural
      design elements that feel personal and inviting.
    </p>

    <p>
      Popular wedding venues and settings for this style include desert venues,
      garden spaces, outdoor estates, ranches, vineyards, mountain lodges,
      backyard weddings, and destination celebrations.
    </p>

    <h2>Popular Boho Wedding Invitation Styles</h2>

    <ul>
      <li>Earthy boho wedding invitations</li>
      <li>Wildflower wedding invitation suites</li>
      <li>Desert boho wedding stationery</li>
      <li>Neutral wedding invitations</li>
      <li>Terracotta and rust wedding invitations</li>
      <li>Botanical wedding invitations</li>
      <li>Boho minimalist wedding invitations</li>
      <li>Outdoor wedding invitation suites</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Designed for Relaxed, Intentional Weddings</h2>

    <p>
      Our boho invitation suites are created for couples who want wedding stationery
      that feels beautiful without feeling overly formal. Each suite can include
      save the dates, wedding invitations, RSVP cards, details cards, welcome signage,
      menus, seating charts, and day-of wedding stationery.
    </p>

    <p>
      We focus on cohesive wedding branding that carries your style from the first
      invitation to the final wedding day detail.
    </p>

    <h2>Custom Boho Wedding Stationery</h2>

    <p>
      Looking for something fully custom? We can create a personalized boho wedding
      invitation suite based on your venue, color palette, floral inspiration,
      typography preferences, and overall wedding vision.
    </p>

    <p>
      From soft and romantic to modern and earthy, we help create wedding stationery
      that feels true to your celebration.
    </p>

    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <h3>What is a boho wedding invitation style?</h3>
    <p>
      Boho wedding invitations are inspired by natural textures, earthy colors,
      romantic florals, relaxed layouts, and artistic details. The style often feels
      organic, warm, creative, and personal.
    </p>

    <h3>Are boho wedding invitations customizable?</h3>
    <p>
      Yes. Colors, fonts, wording, layouts, illustrations, and wedding details can
      all be customized.
    </p>

    <h3>Do you offer matching wedding day stationery?</h3>
    <p>
      Yes. Matching welcome signs, menus, seating charts, escort cards, and other
      day-of paper goods can be designed to match your invitation suite.
    </p>

    <h3>Do you offer printed and digital invitations?</h3>
    <p>
      We offer both digital invitation designs and professionally printed wedding stationery.
    </p>

  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
